          "title": "",
          "textContent": "We are located in the historic center of Rosia Montana 331. The building was a bank, medical center, cinema and then it was bought by our grandparents who work in mining industry, and used for living. It's a heritage building, so we preserved the painting, the wooden floor, the windows, the heating with terracotta stoves, but we also added new bathrooms and kitchen. Te rooms have separate entries connected by a yard with hammocks, green grass and a nice view to the Cânic massif."
